---
title: Tuscan Baked Salmon & Veggie Fries with Chargrilled Capsicum Mayo & Apple-Almond Salad
description: A fresh salmon is something to get excited about when it comes to dinnertime. String up the balloons and shout hooray when the salmon is drizzled in a delightful chargrilled capsicum mayo because it’s going to be a celebration for your tastebuds!

